    <item>
      <title>高盛因最新刺激措施上调中国经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/goldman-sachs-upgrades-china-growth-forecasts-on-latest-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京方面出台一系列促进经济增长的措施（包括周末宣布的增加公共支出的计划）之后，高盛集团上调了对中国 2024 年和 2025 年经济增长的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/goldman-sachs-upgrades-china-growth-forecasts-on-latest-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 01:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市投资者对中国经济刺激计划持谨慎态度：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/asian-investors-wary-as-china-briefing-underwhelms-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末财政部的简报令投资者失望，而工厂价格的下跌加剧了人们对经济的担忧，导致中国股市波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/asian-investors-wary-as-china-briefing-underwhelms-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 22:21:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度经济调整之际，Infosys 和 Wipro 面临超越预期的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/pressure-amps-up-on-infosys-wipro-to-beat-estimates-amid-india-correction-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者越来越担心潜在的市场调整，印孚瑟斯公司 (Infosys Ltd.)、威普罗公司 (Wipro Ltd.) 和 HCL 科技公司 (HCL Technologies Ltd.) 的股价都遭遇了高预期。]]></description>
